<h2 id="방식">방식</h2>

<p>예전에 만들 당시는 data-* 속성을 이용해서 vertical 구조로 만들었습니다.</p>

<hr />
<div>
    <button>A type</button>
    <button>B type</button>
    <button>B type</button>
</div>
<div class="d-flex flex-column">
    <span class="alert alert-dark">Card 1</span>
    <span class="alert alert-dark">Card 2</span>
    <span class="alert alert-dark">Card 3</span>
    <span class="alert alert-dark">Card 4</span>
